https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26765,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/19\/offering-not-cut-hair-nails\/","url_meta":{"origin":25299,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Those offering sacrifices not cut hair or nails","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the ten days of Dhul Hijjah begin and one of you intends to sacrifice, let him not remove anything from his hair or skin.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1977 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Nawawi said, \u201cThe\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26866,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/11\/17\/shafii-desire-no-praise\/","url_meta":{"origin":25299,"position":4},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: I desire no praise or credit for teaching","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 17, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Hatim reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI never debated anyone and loved for him to be wrong. There is no knowledge in my heart but that I wish everyone could have it and attribute none of it to me.\u201d Source: A\u0304da\u0304b al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304 wa Mana\u0304qibuh\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"im